Live proof — hybrid code_search (BM25 + embeddings + graph, RRF fusion)
========================================================================

Setup: pirs on its OWN repo, LLM = DeepSeek (deepseek-v4-flash), embeddings =
local Ollama all-minilm (384-dim). Flags: --semantic --embed-model all-minilm
--embed-max-chars 512 --embed-batch-cap 4000. Cold DB wiped first; the run
embedded all 2124/2124 symbols (verified in .pirs/graph.db). API key scrubbed;
no key appears in this log or the raw capture.

The tool reports which arms fired in brackets: [lexical+semantic+graph].

------------------------------------------------------------------------
Query 1 (natural language — the SAME query as log 13's semantic-only run):
  "decide whether a source file has changed and needs re-parsing for
   incremental indexing or staleness detection"

> code_search
