embedding-cosine alone does not guarantee.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
What this proves live, end to end:
  - BM25 (tantivy) + embedding cosine + graph centrality fuse via RRF (k=60).
  - The [lexical+semantic+graph] tag confirms all three arms contributed.
  - --embed-batch-cap indexed all 2124 symbols in one pass with a fast model;
    default (256/call) keeps a first search from blocking on a cold index.
  - Fully graceful: with no --semantic the same tool runs [lexical+graph]; unit
    tests cover a dead embedding service (falls back to lexical) and an
    oversized chunk (truncated per-item, not fatal).

------------------------------------------------------------------------
